<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
  <meta content='text/html; charset=UTF-8' http-equiv='Content-Type' />
</head>
<body>
  <h1>Registration Update</h1>
  
  <p>Dear <%= @registration.provider_name %>,</p>
  
  <p>Thank you for your interest in joining our provider network. After careful review, we regret to inform you that we are unable to approve your registration for <strong><%= @registration.category.humanize %></strong> services at this time.</p>
  
  <% if @registration.rejection_reason.present? %>
    <p><strong>Reason:</strong> <%= @registration.rejection_reason %></p>
  <% end %>
  
  <p>This decision does not necessarily reflect on the quality of your services. We encourage you to:</p>
  <ul>
    <li>Review the requirements for your service category</li>
    <li>Ensure all required information is complete and accurate</li>
    <li>Consider reapplying in the future</li>
  </ul>
  
  <p>If you have questions about this decision or would like to discuss your application further, please contact us.</p>
  
  <p>We appreciate your understanding and wish you the best in your practice.</p>
  
  <p>Best regards,<br>
  The Autism Services Locator Team</p>
</body>
</html> 